By: T'u Lung
---
He who has attained the Tao can go into water without becoming wet, jump into
fire without being burned, walk upon reality as if it were a void and travel on
a void as if it were reality. He can be at home wherever he is and be alone in
whatever surroundings. That is natural with him.
